<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.1.7">
<l>cevvaratta vuṭaiyāṭai yataṉmēlōr civaḷikaikkac ceṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>avvaratta vaṭiyiṇaiyu maṅkaikaḷum paṅkayamē yeṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>maivaḷarkkum maṇiyuruvam marakatamō maḻaimukilō veṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>kaivaḷarkku maḻalāḷar kaṇṇapurat tammāṉaik kaṇṭāḷ kollō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“Over his rosy red  cloth garment is a waist sash,” she declares;</l>
<l>“Both of those reddened feet and lovely hands are [like] lotuses,”</l>
<l rend="indent">she declares;</l>
<l>“Is his jewel[-like] beauty, which intensifies darkness, that of an emerald</l>
<l rend="indent">	or of rainclouds?” she wonders.</l>
<l>Did she see the lord of Kaṇṇapuram where keepers of the fire</l>
<l rend="indent">foster [it] by hand?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
